odeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "a07d2fbe-5411-4eb4-8769-b001b22c7ce8", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "b4191f35e817418cf2ad785429f2b4fb7667a6d32273834f6ae5c2a94be0105a", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "CONFIDENTIAL INFORMATION OBLIGATIONS\n\nIn consideration of each party disclosing its Confidential Information to the other party for the Purpose, the Recipient must ensure that Confidential Information is:\n\n\uf0b7 maintained  confidential  with  at  least  the  standard  of  care  that  the  Recipient maintains to protect its own confidential information;\n\n\uf0b7 not disclosed to any Unauthorised Person;\n\n\uf0b7 only used for the Purpose;", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2035, "end_char_idx": 2461, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "a07d2fbe-5411-4eb4-8769-b001b22c7ce8": {"__data__": {"id_": "a07d2fbe-5411-4eb4-8769-b001b22c7ce8", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "28e9b00e-249f-4888-8237-afc74b996cdb", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "0f31cf9b89d10872dfd20141c19ff6f55f4ca5222f8ab8aa5366a11db84384ac", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "593b7e7f-33c7-415d-8a54-ec3c9f0b5d62", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "18a0d37f66d23907ae311d62d6b9ac107fc504e139f593ab5aeabdb90ce45871", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "8ce7532d-ebd8-476a-bb97-f6a15e4ac270", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "1bef290adc12526d80fd1c2cdb9c2254cd25f993f2317b5f6ae90d1ffb4967f2", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "and \uf0b7 not reproduced in any form except as required for the purpose.The Recipient must ensure that access to Confidential Information is only given to those of  its  officers,  employees  and  advisers  who  require  access  for  the  Purpose,  and  that those officers, employees and advisers are informed of the confidential nature of the Confidential Information  and  keep that information  confidential.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2464, "end_char_idx": 2872, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "8ce7532d-ebd8-476a-bb97-f6a15e4ac270": {"__data__": {"id_": "8ce7532d-ebd8-476a-bb97-f6a15e4ac270", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "28e9b00e-249f-4888-8237-afc74b996cdb", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "0f31cf9b89d10872dfd20141c19ff6f55f4ca5222f8ab8aa5366a11db84384ac", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "a07d2fbe-5411-4eb4-8769-b001b22c7ce8", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "b4191f35e817418cf2ad785429f2b4fb7667a6d32273834f6ae5c2a94be0105a", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "75bdbb31-a129-43f3-a8da-2ac246bb2905", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "7441072a4bb8e099e3fedbd083138e5e0d991d851a48096177aec9307eee9644", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Parties  to  whom  the information is imparted must be warned that included \u2018insider information,\u2019 regarding publicly listed and traded shares may preclude them from such trade in those shares.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2876, "end_char_idx": 3069, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "75bdbb31-a129-43f3-a8da-2ac246bb2905": {"__data__": {"id_": "75bdbb31-a129-43f3-a8da-2ac246bb2905", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "28e9b00e